entry.def: Someone or something that is archetypal has all the most important characteristics of a particular kind of person or thing and is a perfect example of it.

example.ex: Cricket is the archetypal English game.
example.tran: 板球是典型的英格兰运动。

means.word_mean: 1. representing or constituting an original type after which other similar things are patterned;
